@node History "History"
@next Register
@prev Copyright
@{b} History @{ub}

    v2.2        A Minor Update.

                    *   Fixed bug in OutDir which conflicted  with  OutFile
                        and caused crashes.

    v2.1        A Minor Update.

                    *   Fixed bug in Multi Input selection.

                    *   Added Quiet button to Workbench GUI.

                    *   Added OutDir so Multiple Encoded/Decoded files  are
                        no  longer  placed  in  the  same  directory as the
                        Scrambler executable.

    v2.0        Another complete rewrite especially for  registered  owners
                of v1.2. Many new features added.

                    *   Keyboard shortcuts for gadgets on the workbench GUI.

                    *   Multiple Input files  can  now  be  placed  into  a
                        single file or into seperate files.

    v1.2        This is practically a complete rewrite so that the features
                bolted on in v1.1 are now fully integrated into the program
                and not just a quick hack.

    v1.1        Added a few of things suggested by Bill Beogelein and fixed
                some bugs.

                o   Removed extra 'BEGIN' before "--- CUT HERE ---" and the
                    approximate debug info.

                o   Restored the  CLI  Interface which I had removed. Don't
                    ask me why I removed  it  because I  can't remember but
                    it's back. =)

                o   No longer tells the user that  its  about to "overwrite
                    this  file"  and  then  only  give  them  1 choice: OK.
                    Now theres a choice to CANCEL the operation.
                    Thanks Bill. =)

    v1.0        First release of Scrambler.
                (5th March 1996)

    v0.9        Optomised Decoding Routine, now 600% faster.
                Not released. (3rd Mar 1996)

    v0.8        Optomised Encoding Routine, now 500% faster.
                Not released. (2nd Mar 1996)

    v0.7        Added Overwrite & Table Output.
                Not released. (1st Mar 1996)

    v0.6        Disabled Multiple Files due to bug. Will be active and fixed in
                Registered Version.
                Not released. (29th Feb 1996)

    v0.5        Added Asl.library support.
                Not released. (27th Feb 1996)

    v0.4        Fixed bug in Outfile String gadget.
                Not released. (25th Feb 1996)

    v0.3        Added GUI & removed CLI interface.
                Not released. (23rd Feb 1996)

    v0.2        Added XXEncoding/XXDecoding.
                Not released. (22nd Feb 1996)

    v0.1        CLI based UUEncoding/UUDecoding version (Slow & Unreliable)
                Not released. (20th Feb 1996)


@endnode

